line=21 fonts=F1-11.0,F1-14.0,F3-14.0 bbox=90.72,331.45,352.78,345.44 iscore=0.38 :      c. possessed nouns: λy λx [N(x) & POSS(y,x)]
line=22 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,309.32,538.61,323.3 iscore=0.07                   :The classification of verbs is more intricate: static verbs denoting states have an addi-
line=23 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,293.24,538.61,307.22 iscore=0.14                  :tional time variable t, while dynamic verbs denoting events have an additional situa-
line=24 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,277.1,538.64,291.08 iscore=0.25                   :tion variable s. Intransitive verbs thus have t or s as the referential argument (to be
line=25 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,261.02,538.61,275.0 iscore=0.19                   :bound  by tense) and a further argument to be realized as a complement, while rela-
line=26 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,244.94,538.58,258.92 iscore=0.07          :tional verbs have two complements.  Static intransitives such as sit or dead (whose
line=27 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,228.8,538.64,242.78 iscore=0.15                   :counterpart is an adjective in some languages) can be compared with static relationals
line=28 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,212.72,538.66,226.7 iscore=0.08           :such as surround. For dynamic  verbs, two classificatory factors play a role: inherent
line=29 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,196.64,538.66,210.62 iscore=0.23                  :aspect and inherent control. According to their inherent aspect, verbs can be telic
line=30 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,180.56,538.6,194.54 iscore=0.07           :(such as return or die) or atelic (such as sing or boil). Inherent control distinguishes
line=31 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,164.42,538.59,178.4 iscore=0.12           :whether the verb is agentive (such as return or sing) or non-agentive (such as die or
line=32 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,148.34,502.37,162.32 iscore=0.06          :boil). (2b) illustrates the resulting cross-classification for dynamic intransitives.
line=33 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,126.26,469.69,140.24 iscore=0.30                  :(2)   Classification of intransitive verbs according to their semantic type.
line=34 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=90.72,110.12,153.97,124.1 iscore=0.11                  :      a. static (t)
