line=185 fonts=F1-14.0,F2-14.0 bbox=56.7,287.72,538.59,301.7 iscore=0.20                                                         :Obviously, w- is the active and y- the inactive morpheme, and they realize the direct
line=186 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,270.68,538.73,284.66 iscore=0.33                                                                :vs. inverse setting of transitive verbs. Simultaneously, they also specify of whether an
line=187 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,253.7,367.34,267.68 iscore=0.23                                                                 :intransitive verb is inherently agentive or non-agentive.
line=188 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,232.34,477.32,246.32 iscore=0.29                                                                :(10)  Transitive verbs                                 Intransitive verbs
line=189 fonts=F2-14.0 bbox=90.72,217.34,307.92,231.32 iscore=0.25                                                               :      direct setting         inverse setting
line=190 fonts=F1-14.0,F3-14.0 bbox=90.72,202.34,494.61,216.32 iscore=0.30                                                       :      λy    λx   V(x,y)      λy    λx   V(x,y)         λx V(x)    λy  V(y)
line=191 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=94.18,186.44,458.17,200.42 iscore=0.20                                                               :      3      1                1     3                  1           1
line=192 fonts=F1-11.0 bbox=124.68,171.19,481.24,182.17 iscore=0.00                                                              :            ACT              INACT                    ACT         INACT
line=193 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,148.58,538.58,162.56 iscore=0.00                                                                :The prefix-verb combination does not show  by itself whether the verb is transitive or
line=194 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,131.6,538.6,145.58 iscore=0.29                                                                  :intransitive. Moreover, all intransitive verbs must be classified semantically. That is,
line=195 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,114.62,538.67,128.6 iscore=0.31                                                                 :this type of argument linking heavily hinges on semantic classification and does not
line=196 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,97.58,417.65,111.56 iscore=0.15                                                                 :allow the kind of generalizations that are possible in other types.

