line=298 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,195.92,538.61,209.9             :Note that these features are similar to those proposed in Lexical Mapping Theory by
line=299 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,178.94,538.65,192.92 iscore=0.21:Bresnan and  collaborators: [+hr] corresponds to [+o], and [+ho] corresponds to [+r].
line=300 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,161.9,538.59,175.88 iscore=0.13 :However,  in my account the more specific feature [+ho] is only used in the positional
line=301 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,144.92,438.89,158.9 iscore=0.20 :type, in contrast to [+r], which is meant to be universally applicable.

