line=322 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,411.8,538.63,425.78 iscore=0.08                                                                :Furthermore, both objects can become  subject under passive (still with two interpre-
line=323 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,394.82,538.63,408.8 iscore=0.53                                                                :tations), and also can be marked with object affixes on the verb (not shown here).
