line=457 fonts=F1-11.0 bbox=73.68,98.29,538.58,109.27 iscore=0.06                                                             :    Here, the reversal of setting is also expressed by different positions of the corresponding nouns in the
line=458 fonts=F1-11.0 bbox=73.68,85.27,538.63,96.25 iscore=0.37                                                              :    syntax (see footnote 2), but this is not necessary for Navajo because the affixes on the verb already sat-
line=459 fonts=F1-11.0,F2-11.0 bbox=73.68,72.31,538.6,83.3 iscore=0.32                                                        :    isfy the arguments. The yi-/bi- prefixes can also be used for reference tracking, similarly to the obviative
line=460 fonts=F1-11.0 bbox=73.68,59.29,175.7,70.27 iscore=0.06                                                               :    suffixes in Plains Cree.

