line=468 tag=G span_id=101-29 lang_name=Plains Cree lang_code=crk fonts=F1-11.0,F1-14.0 bbox=107.67,651.97,454.99,665.96 iscore=1.00:         man       dog-OBV     see-DIRECT    CONJUNCT-leave-3OBV
line=469 tag=T span_id=101-29 lang_name=Plains Cree lang_code=crk fonts=F1-14.0,F1-9.0 bbox=107.7,635.0,312.11,650.96 iscore=0.25   :        ‘The man  saw the dog_{obv} as it_{obv} left’
line=470 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,614.18,538.66,628.16 iscore=0.13                                                                   :It is still an open question why the inverse type of argument linking, as demonstrated
line=471 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,597.2,538.56,611.18 iscore=0.20                                                                    :by the Algonquian languages, is only rarely found among the languages of the world.
line=472 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,580.22,538.59,594.2 iscore=0.14                                                                    :It might be computationally too a complex type, which is disfavored because of in-
line=473 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,563.18,538.57,577.16 iscore=0.21                                                                   :herent problems, or the invention of an inverse morpheme might be very improbable
line=474 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,546.2,313.72,560.18 iscore=0.08                                                                    :so that the chance that it happens is quite low.
line=475 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=73.68,529.22,538.65,543.2 iscore=0.12                                                                   :   I turn now to the last type of argument linking to be discussed here, which is by
line=476 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,512.18,538.55,526.16 iscore=0.18                                                                   :far the most dominant type among the languages of the world, and allows for a large
line=477 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,495.2,538.67,509.18 iscore=0.25                                                                    :amount  of variation. It is therefore not a surprise that many linguists believe it to be
line=478 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,479.12,413.96,493.1 iscore=0.12                                                                    :the universal type of argument linking (which I think is wrong).

