line=580 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,151.4,538.55,165.38 iscore=0.00                  :Straits Salish is rather near to this ideal type of split case; the table in (29) shows that
line=581 fonts=F1-11.0,F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,135.25,538.69,149.24 iscore=0.22         :ACC  suffixes exist only for the 1st or 2nd person (as well as for reflexives), while
line=582 fonts=F1-11.0,F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,119.17,538.55,133.16 iscore=0.44         :there is only one ERG suffix for the 3rd person (homonymous with a possessive suf-
line=583 fonts=F1-14.0 bbox=56.7,103.1,80.43,117.08 iscore=0.07                   :fix).

